Altaria (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0333: Swablu
Pokémon
#0335: Zangoose →

Altaria has been featured on 26 different cards since it debuted in the EX Dragon expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Altaria cards are normally Colorless-type or Dragon-type Stage 1 Pokémon. As a Dragon-type, their attacks normally have costs including and Energy.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Altaria

Altaria
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
